  },
  "description": "Aggregates the five active data-plane SLIs from ADR-0012 \u00a72 into a single on-call pane: live p99, rolling 30-day compliance and the p99 trend per SLI.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [
    {
      "title": "ADR-0012 \u2014 Data-plane SLOs, SLIs and error budgets",
      "url": "https://github.com/unnamedlab/OpenFoundry/blob/main/docs/architecture/adr/ADR-0012-data-plane-slos.md",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "external link",
      "targetBlank": true
    }
  ],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## OpenFoundry data-plane SLOs\n\nSingle pane used by on-call to decide whether a freeze is in effect (see [ADR-0012 \u00a73](https://github.com/unnamedlab/OpenFoundry/blob/main/docs/architecture/adr/ADR-0012-data-plane-slos.md#3-error-budgets-monthly-and-freeze-policy)).\n\n* **Current p99** \u2014 `histogram_quantile(0.99, \u2026[5m])` per SLI.\n* **30-day compliance** \u2014 fraction of requests under the p99 bound. Soft freeze \u2265 50 % of monthly budget consumed; hard freeze \u2265 90 %.\n* **p99 trend (6 h)** \u2014 overlay of the live p99 vs the SLO bound; watch for tail drift before the burn-rate alert fires.\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 2,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Flight SQL point query (cache hit)  \u00b7  p99 target **20 ms**  \u00b7  SLO **99.5 %**"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Current p99 (5m)",
      "description": "Rolling-5m p99 latency of the SLI's stock histogram.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "datasource",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "datasource",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(flight_sql_query_duration_seconds_bucket{cache=\"hit\",query_kind=\"point\"}[5m])))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 3,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 0.016
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.02
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "30-day compliance",
      "description": "Fraction of requests under the p99 latency bound over the rolling 30-day window.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "datasource",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "datasource",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(flight_sql_query_duration_seconds_bucket{cache=\"hit\",query_kind=\"point\",le=\"0.020\"}[30d])) / sum(rate(flight_sql_query_duration_seconds_count{cache=\"hit\",query_kind=\"point\"}[30d]))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "decimals": 4,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 0.99
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0.995
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto"
      }
    },
